```typescript
interface ConversationScenario {
  id: string;
  title: string;           // "At the Restaurant"
  description: string;     // "Order food and interact with staff"
  difficulty: 'beginner' | 'intermediate' | 'advanced';
  context: string;         // Cultural background info
  dialogues: Dialogue[];
}

interface Dialogue {
  speaker: 'you' | 'other';
  greek: string;
  english: string;
  options?: string[];      // Response choices
  correctOption?: number;
  explanation?: string;    // Why this response is appropriate
}
```

**Scenarios to Include**:
